narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: A great new knowledge about the 1960s in Latin America, theoretical tools to understand questions in this context. Through the reading list, I discovered great texts that are helpful for my future career.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: A wonderful instructor and an excellent TA present a historic and theoretical panorama in a comprehensible way and invite to engage in intensive discussions. I would recommend this course for everyone!

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes, because this course is a jewel regarding the supervision by the instructor and TA! It helps to apprehend the movement of the 1960s, invites to read texts in original languages and to open the theoretical horizon.
